You are helping build Cosmic Curiosity Agent.

Project goal:
- Build an AI-powered educational agent for universe and space "what if" questions.
- Keep explanations scientific, simple, cinematic, and engaging.
- Keep output structured every time.
- Do not expose API keys or secrets.
- Do not commit .env.
- Use environment variables for API keys.
- Keep code beginner-friendly.
- Preserve project structure unless necessary.

Agent output should include:
- Short Answer
- Scientific Breakdown
- Reality Score out of 10,000
- Danger Level
- Imagination Scene
- Fun Facts
- Final Verdict